data.Name: description
data.Label: Please answer the following questions about ALL of the headaches you have had over the last 3 months. Enter 0 if you did not have the activity in the last 3 months. Please take the completed form to your healthcare professional.

data.Name: Middle Initial
data.Label: 1. On how many days in the last 3 months did you miss work or school because of your headaches?

data.Name: Middle Initial
data.Label: 2. How many days in the last 3 months was your productivity at work or school reduced by half or more because of your headaches? (Do not include days you counted in question 1 where you missed work or school.)

data.Name: Middle Initial
data.Label: 3. On how many days in the last 3 months did you not do household work (such as housework, home repairs and maintenance, shopping, caring for children and relatives) because of your headaches?

data.Name: Middle Initial
data.Label: 4. How many days in the last 3 months was your productivity in household work reduced by half or more because of your headaches? (Do not include days you counted in question 3 where you did not do household work.)

data.Name: Middle Initial
data.Label: 5. On how many days in the last 3 months did you miss family, social or leisure activities because of your headaches?
